info.name: Masala Dosa- No Onion No Garlic
info.description: Mashed potatoes fried with flavorful south indian spices and entangled into dosa with love and care. All the items including sambar are prepared without onion and garlic. Served with sambar and coconut chutney

info.name: Rava Masala Dosa- No Onion No Garlic
info.description: Mashed potatoes fried and topped up with south indian spices, wrapped into semolina base dosa encompassing taste and health at one place. All the items including sambar are prepared without  onion and garlic. Served with sambar and coconut chutney

info.name: Plain Dosa- No Onion No Garlic
info.description: Simplicity always wins hearts. Enjoy this delectable plain dosa served with sambar and coconut chutney without worrying about onion or garlic. All the items including sambar are prepared without onion without garlic

info.name: Rava Plain Dosa- No Onion No Garlic
info.description: For the health seekers, we bring the goodness of semolina. Binge upon this south indian dosa in rava base without worrying about onion or garlic . This is served with sambar and coconut chutney. All the items including sambar are prepared without onion without garlic

info.name: Vada (2pcs)- No Onion No Garlic
info.description: Now have your crispy vada without worrying about onion and garlic. Served with sambar and coconut chutney. All the items including sambar are prepared without  onion and garlic.

info.name: Idli (2pcs) - No Onion No Garlic

info.description: Idli fried with sambar in authentic south indian style.(2 pcs). All the preparations are made without onion and garilic

info.name: Mix Veg Uttapam- No Onion No Garlic
info.description: Uttapam topped with delicious blend of veggies like carrot, capsicum, beans etc in flavorful spices. Served with sambar and coconut chutney. All the items including sambar are prepared without  onion and garlic.

info.name: Masala Uttapam- No Onion No Garlic
info.description: Uttapam topped with spicy mashed potato masala. Served with sambar and coconut chutney. All the items including sambar are prepared without  onion and garlic.

info.name: Rava Masala Dosa
info.description: Rava based dosa with masala made of mashed potatoes fried delicately with veggies and spices. Masala given separate. Served with spicy sambar, modest coconut chutney and fiery onion tomato chutney

info.name: Rava Butter Masala Dosa
info.description: Amul butter on your all time favourite rava masala dosa. Masala given separate. Served with spicy sambar, modest coconut chutney and fiery onion tomato chutney

info.name: Rava Paneer Masala Dosa
info.description: Amul paneer slightly sauted with mashed potatoes gives a great taste with rava dosa. Masala of mashed potatoes and amul paneer given separate . Served with spicy sambar, modest coconut chutney and fiery onion tomato chutney

info.name: Rava Plain Dosa
info.description: Rava based plain dosa prepared authentically with slight hint of species for you. Served with spicy sambar, modest coconut chutney and fiery onion tomato chutney

info.name: Lemon Rice
info.description: Perfectly cooked rice tossed with lemon juice, peanuts, curry leaves and our special South Indian spices. Served with spicy Sambar, cruchy Papad and tangy pickle

info.name: Sambar Rice
info.description: Flavoured rice moderately fried in Sambar and tossed with south Indian style tadka will make your crave for more. Served with crunchy Papad and Red Chutney

info.name: Curd Rice
info.description: Perfect amalgamation of healthy curd and rice tossed with curry leaves and authentic spices will not let you forget the taste. Served with tangy Pickle, crunchy Papad and Red Chutney

info.name: Tomato Rice
info.description: Rice cooked to perfection with tangy tomatoes, curry leaves and authentic spices will metl your heart. Served with spicy Sambar, Coconut Chutney, crunchy Papad and Red Chutney

info.name: Coconut Rice
info.description: Coconut is one of the most nutritious food of our mother nature. Taste the flavours of coconut, in this south indian delicacy where rice falls in love with finely grated coconut . Served with spicy sambar, crunchy papad and red chutney

info.name: Payasam
info.description: Sweet flavourful kerala style dessert, prepared lovingly with rice and melting jaggery can be a great companion in winters. (250g)

info.name: Chole Bhature
info.description: Golden bhatures(2pcs) served with spicy chole can be a great food choice in your food cravings, accompanied with sliced onions and pickle.

info.name: Pav Bhaaji
info.description: What can be more lovely with pav bhaji cushioned in amul butter. The fluffy pav served with super spicy, tangy and buttery bhaji can be a great roller coaster ride of taste and flavours for you. Accompanied with chopped onions and lemon slice, it is definitely a mood changer.

info.name: Rasam Vada
info.description: What can be more delicious than vada(2pcs) dipped in flavourful rasam. Rasam is a south indian speciality that is tangy in flavour. Not only it is immensely soothing and delicious, but is also loaded with health benefiting properties as well.

info.name: Pizza Idli
info.description: When east met west, it gave birth to idli pizza. Idli topped with sweet corn, paneer, onion, capsicum and loaded with cheese and our special sauce.

info.name: Rasam Idli
info.description: 2 pcs idli dipped in our spicy rasam can be a great go to meal. Rasam is a south indian speciality that is tangy in flavour. Not only it is immensely soothing and delicious, but is also loaded with health benefiting properties as well.

info.name: Gajar Ka Halwa
info.description:
We bring to you the national dessert of india, our special gajar ka halwa. Carrots cooked with all our love in loads of fatty milk , desi ghee, premium dry fruits and sugar will surely give you a delectable experience.
(quantity - 250 gms)

info.name: Rasam
